com.navis.framework.persistence

Interface IBusinessContextStatsFacade

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusinessContextStatsFacade

    public interface IBusinessContextStatsFacade
    It works for Oracle 10 and 11 only. Other databases will ignore this.

    This interface provides ability to embed business context information into database connection. Standard Oracle reports (like ASH) will show session history statistics by logged user name.

    Author:
    Andrey Ignatenko, Jun 18, 2010
